</p></td>
<td  width="187"  bordercolor="#DBD6D3" bgcolor="#F3F3F3" border="0"  alt=""><p style="margin-top:2.0pt; margin-right:5.0pt; margin-bottom: 2.0pt; margin-left:5.0pt; text-align:left;"><span class="style28"><b>Weichai (Tecnología Deutz)</b></span>

<td  width="219"  bordercolor="#DBD6D3" bgcolor="#F3F3F3" border="0"  alt=""><p style="margin-top:2.0pt; margin-right:5.0pt; margin-bottom: 2.0pt; margin-left:5.0pt; text-align:left;"><span class="style28">TOLVA SEMIROQUERA</span></p></td>

<td  width="187"  bordercolor="#DBD6D3" bgcolor="#F3F3F3" border="0"  alt=""><p style="margin-top:2.0pt; margin-right:5.0pt; margin-bottom: 2.0pt; margin-left:5.0pt; text-align:left;"><span class="style28">EURO III</span></p></td>
